extensionMeta.name: Sheet Navigation & Actions
extensionMeta.description: Sense Sheet Navigation + Actions visualization extension for Qlik Sense.
extensionMeta.author: Stefan Walther

qDef.qDef:
Pick
(
    [%SynHeadersThree_EMC]
    ,
	(
    	Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
    	+
        Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order MT])
    )
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month1)
    
    , $(v_Budget_MT_Month1)
    , $(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month1) - $(v_Budget_MT_Month1)
    , $(v_Forecast_MT_Month1)
    , $(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month1) - $(v_Forecast_MT_Month1)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month2)
	,$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_2MonthsOnward)
    ,
    (
      (
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
          +
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order MT])
      )
      +$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month1)
      +$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month2)
      +$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_2MonthsOnward)
    )
    
)

Pick
(
    [%SynHeadersThree_EMC]
    ,
	(
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
          +
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
    )
    
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month1)
     ,$(v_Budget_Amount_Month1)
      , $(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month1)- $(v_Budget_Amount_Month1)
     ,$(v_Forecast_Amount_Month1)
     , $(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month1)- $(v_Forecast_Amount_Month1)
     
	,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month2)
    
	,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_2MonthsOnward)
    ,
    (
      (
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
          +
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
      )
      +$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month1)
      +$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month2)
      +$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_2MonthsOnward)
    )
)/1000

            +
            Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order MT])
        )
        +$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month1)
        +$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month2)
        +$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_2MonthsOnward)
      )
   )
